works.description: What’s left to see now? Here comes the world’s most expensive diaper pail fit for royalty. Munchkin, designer and manufacturer of baby products, has now taken wraps off the world’s first luxury diaper disposal system - The Royal Diaper Pail by Munchkin. The bling-bling diaper pail is made from solid 24-karat gold and decked out with more than 5,000 rubies, sapphires and diamonds. It also neutralizes diaper odors with a patented system. Moreover, there will be a salaried, 24-hour nursery attendant to help the millionaire parents change their baby’s diapers
